<dl id="n42026d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42026d">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42026d"> 26(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> public confession</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">When the Holy Fathers of the first centuries speak of &ldquo;confession,&rdquo; they invariably understand &ldquo;public confessions,&rdquo; and not auricular confession. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 127</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
